So simple, really

Four steps to freedom.

That's all it takes. IWantLinux handles the hard parts so you don't have to.

01
Pick your distro

Choose from four beginner-friendly Linux versions, each with a plain-English description to help you decide.

02
We download it

IWantLinux downloads the latest official ISO directly. No hunting for files, no sketchy mirrors.

03
Plug in your USB

Grab a USB drive that's 8GB or larger. IWantLinux will detect it automatically and write the installer to it.

04
Restart & enjoy

Leave the USB plugged in, restart your computer, and follow the on-screen prompts. You're done!
